<body>
    <h1>Introduction</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>This document describes the use cases for the IAM platform. The =
IAM platform will handle Associate and Non-Employee Party (NEP) lifecycle m=
anagement (LCM) as well as the overall governance process as described in t=
his requirement document.</p>
<p>This document focuses on:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Definition and validation of scope for the Voyager program.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Alignment of stakeholders=E2=80=99 expectations to secure their involvem=
ent in the delivery of the Voyager program.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Establishing logistics needed for the delivery of the Voyager program =
=E2=80=93 people and processes.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"Introduction-1.1TargetAudience"><strong>1.1 Target Audience</stro=
ng></h3>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;">The following lists the intended audience=
 for this document:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Security Team</p></li>
<li>
<p>Application Owners</p></li>
<li>
<p>QA (Quality Assurance) Team</p></li>
<li>
<p>Voyager Project Team</p></li>
<li>
<p>Project Stakeholders</p></li>
<li>
<p>Core HR Team</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"Introduction-1.2Scope"><strong>1.2 Scope</strong></h3>
<p>The following lists the items to be implemented as part of Ascension Hea=
lth Alliance Voyager program:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Integrate SailPoint IdentityIQ (IIQ) with Oracle Human Capital Managemen=
t Cloud (Oracle HCM Cloud as the authoritative source.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Integrate IIQ with Active Directory (42 domains), ServiceNow, UKG/Kronos=
, Oracle Enterprise Resource Planning Cloud (Oracle ERP Cloud), Oracle EPM =
Cloud, OCI, and OIM for user account and access management.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Establish rules to define the mappings of identity attributes between th=
e target and source systems.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Configure the following LCM processes for Associates and NEP users.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Pre-Hire</p></li>
<li>
<p>New-Hire</p></li>
<li>
<p>Mover</p></li>
<li>
<p>Termination</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Severance</p></li>
<li>
<p>Divesture</p></li>
<li>
<p>Layoff</p></li>
<li>
<p>Resignation</p></li>
<li>
<p>Voluntary termination</p></li>
<li>
<p>Involuntary termination</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li>
<p>Suspension</p></li>
<li>
<p>Leave Of Absence (LOA)&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Manual access provisioning/de-provisioning</p></li>
<li>
<p>Re-hire</p></li>
<li>
<p>Conversion</p></li>
<li>
<p>Profile update&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Provisioning secondary work relationships</p></li>
<li>
<p>
<del>Secondary work relation suspension</del></p></li>
<li>
<p>
<del>Secondary work relation termination&nbsp;</del></p></li>
</ol>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Configure the following LCM process for Non-Worker users:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<p>Non-Worker user onboarding</p></li>
<li>
<p>Non-Worker user offboarding (termination)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li>
<p>Configure request-based access provisioning process with required forms =
and workflows to manage ad-hoc user access requests for in-scope applicatio=
ns.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Develop scripts for unit testing, System Integration Testing (SIT) and U=
ser Acceptance Testing (UAT).</p></li>
<li>
<p>Perform execution for Unit Testing, SIT and Provide guidance for UAT exe=
cution.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Configure access certification for required roles and permissions for Ac=
tive Directory (42 domains), ServiceNow, UKG, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EPM =
Cloud, OCI.</p></li>
<li>
<p>IIQ will generate a feed file in the format which will be agreed upon wi=
th the IAM and OIM team. The feed will be generated on a predefined frequen=
cy and transferred to the OIM system via a defined file transfer mechanism.=
 Feed generation frequency and file transfer mechanism will need to be deci=
ded.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 id=3D"Introduction-1.3Outofscope"><strong>1.3 Out of scope</strong></h3=
>
<ul>
<li>
<p>As part of the Ascension Health Alliance Voyager program, ServiceNow tic=
ket creation is not included.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Disconnected applications provisioning/deprovisioning from SailPoint is =
out of scope.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Execution of UAT scripts is out of scope.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Regression testing for existing functionalities will be performed by Asc=
ension Health Alliance.</p></li>
<li>
<p>UKG account management (i.e., create, enable, disable, delete) is out of=
 scope.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Target applications integrated in OIM will not be managed by SailPoint.<=
/p></li>
<li>
<p>Fixing gaps in the existing SailPoint IIQ platform is out of scope.</p><=
/li>
</ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
